## 🛠️ Requirements

```bash
pip install zeep
```

- `zeep` — SOAP API client for IETT Fleet Management services
- `urllib`, `json`, `xml` — Standard library for REST/JSON/XML APIs

---

## 📡 APIs Used

- **IETT SOAP Web Service** — Fleet management, real-time bus locations
- **IBB Open Data REST API** — Line stops, route information
- Data source: [data.ibb.gov.tr](https://data.ibb.gov.tr/en/)

